<div dir="ltr"><div>What about between nodes? Since this is coming from the OpenIB BTL, would be good to check this. <br><br>Do you know what the MPI thread level is set to when used with the Charm++ runtime? Is it MPI_THREAD_MULTIPLE? The OpenIB BTL is not thread safe.<br>
